                        <td style="padding-left: 8px; text-align: left; vertical-align: bottom; font-size: 18px; color: #cccccc"><a href="tel:1-425-295-7985" style="color: #cccccc; text-decoration: none !important;">+1 (425) 295-6985</a></td>
